WEBVTT

02:34.950 --> 02:36.480 line:80%
you agreed
to pretend to marry into my family

02:36.480 --> 02:37.940 line:80%
and help me keep the house.

02:37.950 --> 02:39.760 line:80%
Pretending to marry into your family

02:39.760 --> 02:42.480 line:80%
is just my way
of repaying your kindness in taking me in.

02:42.480 --> 02:44.390 line:80%
If you have any wishes,

02:44.670 --> 02:45.879 line:80%
you can dream big.
